Salesforce CRM helps to keep track of customers (be it prod or service based company)
Sales , Marketing, orders and services etc.

Why SF CRM is popular than Siebel,SAP etc.. ?
1. Cloud based solution - Just need login ID and password to login
2. In all other crm , thy have infrastructure ... company needs to keep track care of them
3. No need to take that much care fr sec.

Force.com platform used by dev - to cust app - DB integraton,app Int, IDE everything comes by..no need of installation
